)ATTR DEFAULT(%+_)
)BODY Expand(//)
%Tutorial /-/  BOX  /-/ Tutorial
%SELECTION ===>_ZCMD
%                     --------------------------------
                      ×     Edit Macro  "BOX"        ×
                      --------------------------------
+
    This Edit Macro will place "*" around text already in the dataset
    creating a box of "*" around the data. The boxes left hand corner
    will begin where you place the cursor on the screen.

%SYNTAX:+   BOX  width depth
+
+           width is the width of the box (defualt is 20)
+           depth is the depth of the box (defualt is 10)
+
)PROC
     &ZUP = #EMCH
)END
